summary: I've been loving the #drawthisinyourstylechallenge so much that I wanted to do one of my own.  Most of you probably already know...
caption:
I’ve been loving the #drawthisinyourstylechallenge so much that I wanted to do one of my own.

Most of you probably already know how it works, but in case you don’t this is how ^^:
Draw this drawing in your style and post it on instagram with screenshot of my drawing behind it. You can change whatever you want, have fun! And please tag me (or use #biancasierckechallange)! So I can see your beautiful art and so I can share it ♡♡♡
